[*]not hallowed or consecrated
[*]demonic:
extremely evil or cruel; expressive of cruelty or befitting hell;
"something demonic in him--something that could be cruel"; "fires lit
up a diabolic scene"; "diabolical sorcerers under the influence of
devils"; "a fiendish despot"; "hellish torture"; "infernal instruments
of war"; "satanic cruelty"; "unholy grimaces"
[*]sinful: having committed unrighteous acts; "a sinful person"

[/list]
